<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. يَا ذَا الَّذي اتَّخَذَ الزَّمَانَ مَطِيَّةً<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَخُطَا الزَّمَانِ كَثِيرَةُ الْعَثَراتِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>مَاذَا تَقُولُ وَلَيْسَ عِنْدَكَ حُجَّةٌ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>لَوْ قَدْ أَتَاكَ مُنَغِّصُ اللَّذَاتِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>أَوْ مَا تَقُولُ إِذَا حَلَلْتَ مَحَلَّةً<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>لَيْسَ الثِّقَاتُ لأَهْلِهَا بِثِقَاتِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>أَوْ مَا تَقُولُ وَلَيْسَ حُكْمُكَ نَافِذًا<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>فِيمَا تُخَلِّفُهُ مِن التَّرِكَاتِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>مَا مِنْ أَحَبَّ رِضَاكَ عَنْكَ بِخَارِجٍ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>مَا مِنْ أَحَبَّ رِضَاكَ عَنْكَ بِخَارِجٍ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>زُرْتُ الْقُبُورَ قُبُورَ أَهْلِ الْمُلْكِ فِي الدُّ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>نْيَا وَأَهْلِ الرَّتْعِ فِي الشَّهَوَاتِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>كَانُوا مُلُوكَ مَآكِلٍ وَمَشَارِبٍ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>وَمَلابِسٍ وَرَوَائِحٍ عَطِرَاتِ ... &gt;?<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>